<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7539972>
    dc:description "FIGURES 14A–G. Scolopocryptops broelemanni esulcata Attems, 1938; Syntype 1, MY 2063 (NHMW) (photo by Oliver Macek) A head + LBS 1–3, dorsally; B head and forcipular segment, ventrally; C general view, dorsally; D LBS 6–9 (left side), laterally; E LBS 22, 23, legs 21, 22 and basal articles of ultimate legs, ventrally; non-type specimen, MY 8714 (NHMW) F head + LBS 1–3, dorsally; G label of syntypes written by Chagas Junior." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7539972/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7539974>
    dc:description "FIGURES 15A–F. Scolopocryptops broelemanni esulcata Attems, 1938; Syntype 2, MY 2063 (NHMW) (photo by Oliver Macek) A head + LBS 1–3, dorsally; B head and forcipular segment, ventrally; C LBS 6–11, dorsally; D LBS 20–23, dorsally; E LBS 5–11 (right side), laterally; F LBS 21–23, ventrally." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7539974/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7539942>
    dc:description "FIGURES 2A–F. Scolopocryptops rubiginosus C.L. Koch, 1878; SVR.PO.020 A head and LBS 1, dorsally; B head and forcipular segment, ventrally; C LBS 6–10, dorsally; D LBS 6–10, ventrally; Rc 6738 (ZMMU) E head and forcipular segment, ventrally; Rc 6686 (ZMMU) F LBS 7, 8 (right side), laterally." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7539942/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7539950>
    dc:description "FIGURES 5A–F. Scolopocryptops spinicaudus Wood, 1862; SVR.PO.202 A head + LBS 1–3, dorsally; B head, forcipular segment and LBS 1–3, ventrally; C LBS 8–12, ventrally; D LBS 8–12, dorsally; Rc 7165 (ZMMU) E articles 1–6 of right antenna, laterally; Rc 6614 (ZMMU) F LBS 16–23, dorso-laterally." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7539950/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7539960>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9A–D. Scolopocryptops capillipedatus (Takakuwa, 1938); SVR.PH.048 A LBS 21–23, dorsally; B LBS 21–23, laterally; C LBS 20–23, ventrally; D left ultimate leg, medially." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7539960/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7539954>
    dc:description "FIGURES 6A–F. Scolopocryptops spinicaudus Wood, 1862; SVR.PO.202 A LBS 23 and right ultimate leg, laterally; B LBS 21–23 and ultimate legs, ventrally; C right ultimate leg, medially; Rc 7497 (ZMMU) D LBS 7 and 8, laterally; Rc 7225 (ZMMU) E left ultimate leg, dorsally; Rc 7497 (ZMMU) F LBS 13–16, dorsally." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7539954/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

